						<header class="mainheading">
	<hgroup>
		<h1 class="title">Concrete Consequences From Sex Work Stigma<span class="editor" pid="245370"></span></h1>
					<h2  class="subtitle">Criminalization really isn't the root of the problem that sex workers face.</h2>
			</hgroup>
		<p class="byline"><a href="http://reason.com/people/noah-berlatsky/all" rel="author">Noah Berlatsky</a>  | February 8, 2015</p>
  <div class="options">       		
	  
	

