								<section class="relatedtopics">
	<ul>
		<li><a href="http://reason.com/tags/sex-work">Sex Work</a></li>
<li><a href="http://reason.com/tags/prostitution">Prostitution</a></li>
<li><a href="http://reason.com/tags/law-enforcement">Law Enforcement</a></li>
<li><a href="http://reason.com/tags/public-opinion">Public Opinion</a></li>
<li><a href="http://reason.com/tags/criminal-justice">Criminal Justice</a></li>
	
	</ul>
