need to limit sex outside of wedlock. Something that vital and that
has existed for so long doesn't just go away thanks to the
pill.</p>
<p>For valid evolutionary reasons humans and women in particular
are just hard wired to associate sex with commitment and with child
birth. Even if they consciously reject it, the predisposition is
still there. Thus sexual promiscuity usually makes someone unhappy
and people naturally tend to take sex very seriously because of it
is naturally a big deal to them.</p>		</div>
